"guid":"Zjn8nOnGBhqgUl3YEa20lg","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"• Comportamiento (adherencia).","guid":"_W5ONKN-XDsumPByuWJZ4w","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"• Enfermedad (en sí misma).","guid":"iy9ERAPLlnWL9HTvROT8XA","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"0","text":"Paso 1: Determinar si el\\Nestudio es confiable","guid":"h1tPsO8bC8LyAsRFvMfBew","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"Evaluación del uso\\Ndel dispositivo","guid":"CysuzmU1cURjM9erHnUDfg","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"• Tiempo de uso:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• Idealmente >70% en ≥7 días.","guid":"vvxHKHliWZSjoa9FLtIjMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"• Correlación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"• Uso 14 días → correlación fuerte con promedio glucosa\\Núltimos 3 meses, TIR, métrica hiperglucemia (25, 26, 27).","guid":"k2kgpnqDkZ6qs4-U8bIoWA","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"• Días adicionales → no ↑ sustancialmente esta correlación (26).","guid":"iKffExIPhFOzlitwutdTSQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"138","text":"Exactitud de\\Nlos datos","guid":"VbczJh5wSQUzdryF5xDanA","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"• Calibraciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"• Adecuado número de calibraciones pareadas con sensor (idealmente 3-4/día).","guid":"GzR4Z7P80W-X4Gi4d4Tnig","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"• No aplicable a todos los dispositivos (ej. Flash FreeStyle® no requiere calibraciones) (28).","guid":"ZcXMzgEhiQo9iUmaQ55LnA","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"138","text":"Confiabilidad\\Nde datos","guid":"PnRcRHyi36PQdwo_k98E1Q","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"• Determinada por:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"• Adherencia al uso del sensor.","guid":"Nxjrc9bKZSw-msW-J3zylg","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"• Requerimientos específicos de cada tipo de MCG","guid":"w9lKAJaG5K9YSzsqsiHF1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"149","text":"• Falta de confiabilidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Si no se cumple con requisitos de adherencia y exactitud → datos no confiables\\N→ no proceder análisis.","guid":"nwwVjG7yRNnclAQL1l7oiA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"138","text":"Evaluación de fallas\\Nen adherencia","guid":"7PzaB4cqafF4QC7tiGpa2g","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"• Causas\\Ncomunes:","guid":"eggGet-qONaur_xSFqivyA","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• Falta de educación en uso del dispositivo.","guid":"HZMPYtprmUvFB01XxtywLA","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"• Disminución frecuencia escaneos (MCG intermitente).","guid":"_ubK492iuL3Tm0QFSbFDKg","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"• Viajes, estrés, alergias a adhesivos.","guid":"4drs3AFqhpzysDLy5CjmNA","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"156","text":"• Actividad física inusual, enfermedad, uso de esteroides (29).","guid":"Mk-jJ8WBi01y1oYZtH-OBA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"138","text":"Acciones","guid":"Z2aDhs39iuIxBY8mmKW-Gw","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"• Análisis clínico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"• Evaluar situación clínica con el paciente.","guid":"gqovbv7ulWLyl2Z4rJfjbQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"161","text":"• Determinar necesidad de repetir estudio.","guid":"UrZqxaJYGlCj1-WgbX2n5Q","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"161","text":"• Búsqueda de apoyo multidisciplinario (psicología, educador en diabetes) (29).","guid":"5-MszLUDdAzq4mDdfKLmeA","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"138","text":"Objetivos recomendados de TIR en\\Ndiferentes grupos poblacionales","guid":"_IBhV3DkII6Aubd4Q_TFMA","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"1. DM1/DM2","guid":"MFY4PRIBESC6Cp1RZ7TA_Q","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• Meta (mg/dl): 70-180","guid":"Nt-OBeux2AqYfAGNnfdoHQ","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"• TIR %/día: >70% (>16h, 48 min)","guid":"vFN2fZsO-WguVoUkeGPQ7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"• < Meta (mg/dl): <70 y <54","guid":"nSxHDkU0vh_KsldA5vU8Mw","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"• TBR %/día: <4% (<1h) y <1% (<15 min)","guid":"AUuxW_uuxCHkG3e-sEZ2BA","children":[]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"167","text":"• > Meta (mg/dl): >180 y >250","guid":"8qox97NyVH7xft03iJZncw","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• TAR %/día: <25% (<6h) y <5% (<1h, 12 min)","guid":"3ctw0Uo3tEM2N4N1uDeQsg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"166","text":"2. Ancianos,\\Nfrágiles","guid":"pWpfnLe7ngCy9lfX47PD1Q","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"• Meta (mg/dl): 70-180","guid":"s89gR9qDUfTL38wzgq0BfA","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"• TIR %/día: >50% (>12h)","guid":"A0VzVnktKCBBOSN5wRYiaA","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"174","text":"• < Meta (mg/dl): <70","guid":"kntuWjNRgotYNkBQLjsuJw","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"• TBR %/día: <1% (<15 min)","guid":"kmywt2_91HHe35flqh0RvQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"174","text":"• > Meta (mg/dl): >250","guid":"fC0feNuNNpVe4PUMKTc8Pw","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"• TAR %/día: <10% (<2h, 24 min)","guid":"AcrFx_vbLDfJpbTgKaY3Cw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"166","text":"3. DM1 y\\Nembarazo","guid":"LI2xvtt9gozdmAmKvegNIQ","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"• Meta (mg/dl): 63-140","guid":"8p7ZU6C6N0ieVCekn6E_VQ","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"• TIR %/día: >70% (>16h, 48 min)","guid":"ukbBbmFfvNezW1gafZM8Xw","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"• < Meta (mg/dl): <63 y <54","guid":"WX5t8CA70xpToH6xEPw14A","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"• TBR %/día: <4% (<1h) y <1% (<15 min)","guid":"1MLEPJGLybgwLWSeaRvwJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"181","text":"• > Meta (mg/dl): >140","guid":"FYU7OZi0k7BEQQr3cnuJPg","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"• TAR %/día: <25% (<6h)","guid":"d3RpyHZKMDuCVO0JB4RT4A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"166","text":"4. DM2 y\\Nembarazo/DMG","guid":"cJAh2QuFNZx-mVX_0v8D7A","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"• Meta (mg/dl): 63-140","guid":"9Ueh_uH-kIh0Tp1icfKEGg","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"• < Meta (mg/dl): <54","guid":"X2j3MY-_TV5t-z1C5eaYSQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"• > Meta (mg/dl): >140","guid":"o8RDRNtG0AYo9140xxAcKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"166","text":"Nota aclaratoria","guid":"ymr3ilPxAA-B4ntW4-GdjA","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"• TIR: tiempo en rango.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"• TBR: tiempo por debajo del rango.","guid":"YoTgkySLNZolAT8yKYcydw","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"192","text":"• TAR: tiempo por encima del rango.","guid":"4WwLRB_1lPGepg1uPwk3tQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"0","text":"Paso 2: Definir el\\Nproblema o escenario","guid":"sX5bdXn8UWYUCOucQTq9tA","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"Control glucémico\\Na corto plazo","guid":"-350fe8W9_cn9A15IL8a7g","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"• GMI (Glucose\\NManagement Indicator):","guid":"T2T2MtmQILbZzTuGNyQdjg","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• Expresado en %.","guid":"MyOXZqAqS_OpbCblr8af6g","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"• Puede diferir hasta en 81% con HbA1c (31).","guid":"z_EdW9RGEyE5AWVpeLXo7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"• Determina control glucémico a corto plazo.","guid":"FVuEcz7oBuiRjTLPSCc8jQ","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"• Asociación fuerte con HbA1c si datos MCG ≥14 días y preceden a análisis HbA1c en sangre (26).","guid":"rDzq3DTIrMVTVNCNROPrVg","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"198","text":"• Calculado a partir de la media de glucosa MCG.","guid":"qcckNdRE-5VkQhqsg3gc-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"197","text":"• Importante para conocer control glucémico a corto plazo o cuando glicación se ve afectada\\Npor factores no glucémicos (anemia, ferropenia, etnia, disfunción renal).","guid":"QbCw9HsVjoU0UZI29edazQ","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"197","text":"• No usar aisladamente, valorar junto a riesgo de hipoglucemias (4, 32).","guid":"BGSgCbyIwQI73EIrEBAGhQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"196","text":"Objetivos\\Nindividuales y\\Numbrales","guid":"Av-PoXYBB1KdUNHZVLCIVw","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"• TIR (Tiempo en Rango):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• Definido con colores para ilustrar % del tiempo\\Ndentro y fuera del rango objetivo (70-180 mg/dL).","guid":"BpQh_THjAFSOJZNoJ81v2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"209","parent":"206","text":"• Meta: ≥70-75% del tiempo → asociado con HbA1c de 6.7% y menor riesgo de complicaciones (27, 21, 22).","guid":"e83mjwa5iN9wpSqVg6Cn-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"196","text":"Métricas\\Nadicionales","guid":"YprJY9y0A1bAJ5537--r1w","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"• Promedio de glucosa y CV\\N(Coeficiente de Variación):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"• Ayudan a determinar tipo de problema del paciente.","guid":"ZYw9FSRt390H6aESkg8BNg","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"• Triple meta → medicina de precisión en práctica clínica (33, 34).","guid":"ceuu3aVvEf5mqtsZVbIEeA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"196","text":"Problemas o escenarios\\Nmetabólicos (MCG)","guid":"kItrbdTTIEhBhyqVtmuLrA","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"1. Normoglucemia (TIR) – “Más verde”:","guid":"1TUseGWynY5J7rPO436V0w","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"• Difícil alcanzar 100% TIR en tratamiento\\Ncon insulina debido a múltiples variables.","guid":"9hOfQ7tPhlwZjMJ1qxB32w","children":[]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"214","text":"2. Hipoglucemia (TBR) –\\N“Más rojo”:","guid":"jGVCQYcr6hoinXWRN1bgbg","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"• Tiempo debajo del rango.","guid":"lK5G99Y_4p2MYecru4ofXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"214","text":"3. Hiperglucemia (TAR)\\N– “Más amarillo”:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"• Tiempo por encima del rango.","guid":"GWs210k-PF0L3hQipc9F2A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"196","text":"Variabilidad\\Nglucémica","guid":"irEKSxzSdLilhF4tmWhbHg","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"• Registro o segmento\\Nvariable:","guid":"qc7jRSv-jO4LfsZvqaTE0Q","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"• Definido por CV.","guid":"PYGLp8Ke1pkdhss3bqCKDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"221","text":"• CV = (Desviación estándar de glucosa /\\NMedia de glucosa) x 100 (10).","guid":"","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"• CV <36% → baja variabilidad, menor riesgo de complicaciones\\N(estrés oxidativo, hipoglucemias recurrentes) (35, 38, 39).","guid":"RTbqa9RGeJbqxADt9YDR1w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"196","text":"Consideraciones","guid":"1iHx_RH9YRJnEY2Hw4mpKQ","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"• Escenarios no mutuamente excluyentes.","guid":"DL9iar2PP7bpkB3NcmBBbQ","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"• Posible presentación de múltiples escenarios en el mismo paciente ","guid":"wTSYNRCl4ynCi3fhu-XxnA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"0","text":"Paso 3: Determinar\\Ndónde está el problema","guid":"xc6UtNFDRCb5HDIBwsgm8A","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"Identificación del horario del problema","guid":"Lu0UFHu9VP-KjnIaktCfeQ","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"• Gráfica de superposición\\N(AGP):","guid":"0deTJuNSh52aVUA7bXopTQ","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"• Resumen de patrones y tendencias del control glucémico (40).","guid":"VrNmwsUbjTzeM-iY6c4PZQ","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"• Identificación de hipoglucemia (fig. 5).","guid":"QXacTwMVX425bBTeKed0Lg","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"231","text":"• Evaluación de escenarios metabólicos múltiples\\N(ej. hiperglucemia con hipoglucemia y variabilidad)","guid":"MWKWQZrj2WlbS8Wx2OrLPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"235","parent":"229","text":"Caracterización de\\Nhipoglucemia","guid":"KY0n8T7WzEpcCkqOIS-2wg","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"• Frecuencia del evento (patrón en el tiempo).","guid":"C9XzHHSAaHjgvp52gwCNDQ","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"235","text":"• Horario (momento del día).","guid":"xttA820IkwVzz8cm6ZZiNQ","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"235","text":"• Profundidad y duración (severidad por niveles).","guid":"51uvmTd9cEn65hPZzE_RNg","children":[]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"229","text":"• Presencia de hiperglucemias","guid":"RMVSt9WUe7eBWrawJjD1wQ","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"229","text":"• Situaciones de comportamiento mixto (variable)","guid":"a4lagnpSti_tH5Ex7RhV7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"241","parent":"0","text":"Paso 4: Identificar la etiología\\Ndel problema y tratarla","guid":"bmBGzW7-mCdwhZpV0RauNw","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"Identificación\\Nde la causa","guid":"qN7rRvhivXzbsmuu1cY98w","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"• Evaluación de\\Nproblemas con patrón:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"• Repetición en el tiempo.","guid":"PKFAAt8WYis786OcKIlvSg","children":[]}]},{"id":"245","parent":"242","text":"• Eventos clínicamente\\Nsignificativos:","guid":"18QOwg3_rzBu8jssgESUKA","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"• Acción correctiva inmediata (ej. hipoglucemia nivel II y III)","guid":"1QDjp46HTRTPiwz8bt2Tqw","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"245","text":"• Evaluar segmento previo al evento (4-6 horas antes).","guid":"-51Oq13CJgtDs0iv-PMJwg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"241","text":"Captura de factores\\Nde exposición","guid":"7yEkLRzXLh-8xN1L8PM5Dg","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"• Factores a considerar:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"250","parent":"249","text":"• Comidas.","guid":"VeY76GYfhN41tsuY1Iolug","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"249","text":"• Momento del ejercicio.","guid":"4OAhUY9v32WN31Fmr1dHoQ","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"249","text":"• Medicamentos (insulina y temporalidad con comida).","guid":"6S2YNsTDw42xad3LdEZ2yQ","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"249","text":"• Correcciones.","guid":"7qq6OD8ulPq7JcqUnuA4MA","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"248","text":"• Automatización en registros de estos factores sería fundamental (15).","guid":"wzuv64VF-v4Wy33CDAIE3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"255","parent":"241","text":"Esferas limitantes para tratar el\\Nproblema metabólico","guid":"kHUrMLcFWIevl37FBjBXMQ","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"1. Educación\\N(conocimiento):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"• Componente educativo deficitario → mala adherencia a\\Nrecomendaciones dietéticas, conductuales o terapéuticas.","guid":"gCUtzP62AHJsa9QT0194_A","children":[]}]},{"id":"258","parent":"255","text":"2. Comportamiento\\N(autocuidado):","guid":"_yOPQ2-xJbrYO3y2QqwV6g","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"• Automonitoreo y autocontrol.","guid":"OmCtASeTbj7H14TNQfWJIw","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"258","text":"• Adherencia a régimen nutricional,\\Nactividad y medicación.","guid":"SOlwgSyZgr6LHhZXneuGFw","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"255","text":"3. Enfermedad\\N(progresión):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"• Evolución de la enfermedad.","guid":"wHywr-gq-6zGgQoA4A-atA","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"261","text":"• Daño de célula beta, agotamiento de célula alfa.","guid":"zlBcHjPCvmF82nAxwFJ4yQ","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"261","text":"• Complicaciones micro y macrovasculares.","guid":"XmblOOGcvLICbb8-rG2YEQ","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"261","text":"• Requerimiento de basales diferenciales y manejo\\Nespecífico con infusores continuos de insulina.","guid":"SqfMHiOmJOB6-obP5d331Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"241","text":"Acciones correctivas basadas en\\Nrangos IQR e IDR (fig. 7)","guid":"cfUbdy9NqeAQ1X0k14AjOA","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"• Baja variabilidad\\Nen IDR e IQR:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"• Metabólicamente sano.","guid":"vSATrhe-QDQLGhe4fO4myg","children":[]}]},{"id":"269","parent":"266","text":"• Baja variabilidad en IDR, alta\\Nvariabilidad en IQR:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"• Problemas\\Nconductuales.","guid":"aF1QKqo3BQ3bZeUNmBVWJA","children":[]}]},{"id":"271","parent":"266","text":"• Alta variabilidad en IDR, baja\\Nvariabilidad en IQR:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"272","parent":"271","text":"• Dosis de insulina, factor de corrección,\\Ncambios constantes de patrones.","guid":"hY7tg1aXty7XFlU14xJCmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"273","parent":"266","text":"• Alta variabilidad\\Nen IDR e IQR:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"• Problemas de tratamiento\\Ny conductuales.","guid":"A4zIfxC8s5dWJfpUzTAF1g","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"0","text":"Situaciones y acciones correctivas\\Nsegún el tipo de problema","guid":"aj33jxRpON7DtfRSn2f1GA","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"0","text":"1. Hipoglucemia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"277","parent":"276","text":"• Causas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"276","text":"• Sobredosificación de insulina o\\Nmedicamentos hipoglucemiantes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"276","text":"• Insulina basal o\\Nprandial (fig. 5).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"276","text":"• Evaluación:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"276","text":"• Segmento de insulina basal:\\Nmadrugada, omitir alimentos por\\N6-8 horas durante el día.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"276","text":"• Diferencia glucosa al\\Nacostarse y en ayunas →\\Nidentifica sobreinsulinización.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"276","text":"• Tipo y horario\\Nde ejercicio.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"276","text":"• Identificación de hipoglucemias prandiales:\\Nmarcar insulina (10-15 min antes de comida)\\Nen curva de monitoreo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"276","text":"• Evaluación postprandial:\\Ncurvas de descenso, tendencia y\\Nángulos de inclinación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"276","text":"• Bisectriz del ángulo: agudo → gran\\Ndiferencial en índice o sensibilidad;\\Nrecto/obtuso → hipoglucemia tardía.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"276","text":"• Resumen de causas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"276","text":"• Temprana (3-4 h): omisión de bolos, bolos\\Ntardíos, dosis insuficiente, mal conteo de\\Ncarbohidratos, índice, sensibilidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"276","text":"• Tardía (4-6 h): enfermedad renal crónica, alimentos\\Ncon alto contenido de grasa, dietas complejas,\\Ngastroparesia, bolos insuficientes, índice.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"290","parent":"0","text":"2. Hiperglucemia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"291","parent":"290","text":"• Causas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"290","text":"• Exceso de comida,\\Nfalta de insulina.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"290","text":"• Diferenciar segmento\\Nbasal o prandial.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"290","text":"• Picos de excursión postprandial:\\Nángulo más agudo (fig. 7).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"290","text":"• Evaluación:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"290","text":"• Curvas prandiales (3-4 h\\Npost bolo): exactitud de dosis\\Ny tiempo de acción.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"290","text":"• Dosis altas de insulina: curva\\Nde acción más larga.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"290","text":"• Potenciales etiologías:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"290","text":"• Dosis insuficiente de insulina prandial,\\Nbolo tardío o no administrado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"290","text":"• Hiperglucemia con curva en forma\\Nde cúpula y variabilidad (amplios\\Nrangos interdecílicos).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"290","text":"• Resumen de causas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"290","text":"• Temprana (3-4 h): omisión de bolos, bolos\\Ntardíos, dosis insuficiente, mal conteo de\\Ncarbohidratos, índice, sensibilidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"290","text":"• Tardía (4-6 h): enfermedad renal crónica, alimentos\\Ncon alto contenido de grasa, dietas complejas,\\Ngastroparesia, bolos insuficientes, índice.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"304","parent":"0","text":"3. Mixto o variable","guid":"","children":[{"id":"305","parent":"304","text":"• Alta oscilación\\Nglucémica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"306","parent":"304","text":"• Segmento basal: diferencial de\\Nrequerimientos de insulina (ej.\\Nfenómeno del Alba).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"304","text":"• Postprandial: factores inherentes al paciente\\N(conducta, adherencia) o enfermedad (tiempo de\\Nevolución, disfunción de célula beta).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"308","parent":"304","text":"• Identificación:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"309","parent":"304","text":"• Cotejar registros con diario de\\Nalimentos y conductas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"304","text":"• Resumen de causas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"311","parent":"304","text":"• Temprana (3-4 h): omisión de\\Nbolos, bolos agresivos, ejercicio,\\Nsobreinsulinización.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"312","parent":"304","text":"• Tardía (4-6 h): doble bolo en corto tiempo (“stacking”),\\Nbolos agresivos, ejercicio, no adherencia, pobre conteo\\Nde carbohidratos, requerimientos basales diferenciales,\\Nsobrecorrecciones.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"313","parent":"0","text":"Estrategias de intervención según\\Nesfera comprometida (fig. 8)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"314","parent":"313","text":"• Educación\\N(conocimiento):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"313","text":"• Cursos, talleres, soporte nutricional,\\Nempoderamiento, autoevaluación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"316","parent":"313","text":"• Comportamiento\\N(adherencia y autocuidado):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"317","parent":"313","text":"• Entrenamiento, metas medibles,\\Ncuestionarios de seguimiento,\\Nregímenes de tratamiento.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"313","text":"• Enfermedad\\N(progresión):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"319","parent":"313","text":"• EMCG con alarmas, sistemas de infusión continua\\Nde insulina, metas individualizadas, entrenamiento,\\Ncoaching, cursos, talleres.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"320","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"321","parent":"0","text":"17. Nombre del autor. Título del\\Nartículo. Revista, año;\\Nvolumen(número): páginas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"0","text":"40. Nombre del autor. Título del\\Nartículo. Revista, año;\\Nvolumen(número): páginas.","guid":"","children":[]}]},"node_count":322,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"UCI/Medicina Crítica","folder":"Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica","filename":"Monitoreo de glucosa continuo-2024","id":"map_2331","resolved_references":[]}